views.markdown: If you need help with "Essential Utilities (iOS 11+)", you can contact Codey Moore, the developer, via e-mail.
Codey Moore is the maintainer of the package "Essential Utilities (iOS 11+)". Please contact them via email for any questions on this version of the package.
If you found a mistake in the depiction or cannot download the package, you can reach out to the maintainer of the "Codey Moore Repo" repo, Codey Moore.
